<br>
For many many years on Xev Sleeper had the ability to be woken.  We have a rather huge list of guilds capable of taking all 4 warders and waking him up.  But all the guilds on Xev played nice and let him sleep cause at the time, PoP was a bigger challenge, and because they liked the current loot table that exsisted in ST.  <br>
<br>
Trust me when I say if Hawkestone said, &quot;Guys, we are gonna wake Sleeper.&quot; Everyone would snarl a moment and say why??!!  But when it comes down to it they would realize they could not stop them from waking him.  So now, here, is where its stupid to claim that our server wouldnt have all pitched in to help try and be the game's first to do so. <br>
<br>
It wasnt so much that they woke him.  It was that they didnt notify any one, and ran from him after he woke up.  Everyone wanted to be part of it, but how could they when they had no knowledge?  So please, before you say that, know more about how much of a positive server Xev is.  Smaller challenges unite them regularly, Im confident that a big challenge like Sleeper would have drawn them even closer.<br>
